		<platform>all</platform>
		<language></language>
		<summary lang="en">The BitTorrent bencode module as light-weight, standalone package.</summary>
		<description lang="en">This package simply re-packages the existing bencoding and bdecoding implemention from the ‘official’ BitTorrent client as a separate, leight-weight package for re-using them without having the entire BitTorrent software as a dependency.</description>
